11 Section 5. Section 15-70-805, MCA, is amended to read:
12 "15-70-805. Charging station operator statements and tax payment -- rulemaking. (1) All public
13 charging stations must be registered with the department of transportation no later than 30 days after May 19,
14 2023 the first day of operation.
15 (2) When registering the public charging station with the department of transportation, the public
16 charging station owner shall provide the following information:
17 (a) name, mailing address, telephone number, and e-mail address of the owner;
18 (b) street address for the physical location of the public charging station;
19 (c) the public charging station's rated capacity in terms of wattage, voltage, and amperage
20 kilowatts; and
21 (d) additional information as required by the department.
22 (3) Charging stations that begin operation after May 19, 2023, must be registered with the
23 department of transportation no later than 30 days after the first day of operation.
