25 charging station owner and remit the proceeds as calculated in subsection (4)(b) (3)(b) to the department of
26 transportation within 30 days following the preceding calendar quarter when the tax was collected.
27 (b) The public utility shall remit 2.75 cents for each kilowatt hour of electricity sold to a public
28 charging station owner to the department of transportation and is authorized to retain 0.25 cents per kilowatt
